{"tid":160931,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆與的士佬","createTime":"2017-03-18T07:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T20:23:10.000Z","uid":25741,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d12f883361a5dfc902002158466568e06d6bf2dc","tid":160931,"uid":25741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我老豆一路都揸開車出街<br />\n昨日星期五晚佢因為某啲原因<br />\n要係九龍城自己撘的士返屋企<br />\n佢琴晚係whatsapp到咁講:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n**********************<br />\n九龍城D的士全部都是揀客的，正仆街😡<br />\n一個平常的星期五晚上，九龍城的士10架11架停車問你去邊揀客，請問皇家持武和尊貴的立法局議員，你地幾十萬一個月人工做左乜L😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡<br />\n冚旗的士佬問我： 去邊呀？  <br />\n我答： 師父冚旗揀客犯法嫁喎！<br />\n的士師傅話：你外國返來㗎！ 你咁On狗嘅！<br />\n<br />\n真是一個有趣的經驗😆😆😆<br />\n**********************<br />\n<br />\n我一直係到諗究竟邊個先岩呢<br />\n諗左成晚 諗唔通<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 的士揀客正扑街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撘的士係咁架啦 你老豆外國返來架 咁On狗嘅!"},{"pid":"a5f3da4a957ed477fb6a7956d5032118cb04d08b","tid":160931,"uid":25713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"的士佬食屎啦"},{"pid":"756adb91dad3067d3202e4cbb329eb5b20062bb3","tid":160931,"uid":25741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:28:45.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b33ae13a4685795ce8701ce356f8bd886fe586","tid":160931,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"的士狗係咁仆街架啦 你老豆外國番黎？"},{"pid":"3c247843eb09ba1bb3668f2b61e24eb5e119317a","tid":160931,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"拒載咪犯法囉 <br />\n除非個架唔係過海的士 你叫佢過海"},{"pid":"09f999ccb62fe30aa63e2627ef72083c62877a97","tid":160931,"uid":25741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拒載咪犯法囉 <br />\n除非個架唔係過海的士 你叫佢過海</blockquote><br />\n但係佢冚左旗喎"},{"pid":"